<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zì rán jiè měi jǐng shén ài de míng zhèng yǒu shéi cháng lái jì niàn zhǔ zàn měi zhǔ de míng
 wān yán de shān lǐng yáng ér shān pō xíng lán tiān gāo bái yún fēi dào yǐng zài shuǐ zhōng
 shù zhú gān qīng qīng quán shuǐ xiǎng dīng dōng lǜ shù kāi hóng huā bàn niáng shì mì fēng
 hú dié lái fēi wǔ bǎi niǎo yě qí míng rì yuè xīng chén shì hǎo péng yǒu zǒu guò chūn xià qiū dōng
 shēn zāi qí zāi shén wú qióng dà néng fēi niǎo hái méi yǒu zào chū shén zǎo yù bèi tiān kōng
 wǒ bù huì yōu lǜ tā gěi wǒ yǒng shēng sù rán quán rén lái fǔ fú yī shēng róng zhǔ míng</lyrics>
